Package psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher

Interface InteractionEvidenceEnricher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InteractionEnricher<InteractionEvidence>, MIEnricher<InteractionEvidence>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FullInteractionEvidenceEnricher, FullInteractionEvidenceUpdater, MinimalInteractionEvidenceEnricher, MinimalInteractionEvidenceUpdater
    public interface InteractionEvidenceEnricher
extends InteractionEnricher<InteractionEvidence>
    An enricher for interaction evidences. As well as extending the interaction enricher, this also includes an experiment enricher. Experiment is only found in InteractionEvidence .

    24/07/13
